text:
MAC Bare Study paint pot – base
MAC white pigment – lids
MAC Living Pink eyeshadow – crease up to brow bone (discontinued – Sushi Flower is a good alternative)
MAC Passionate eyeshadow – outer v/outer lid
Urban Decay Hotpants eyeshadow (MAC Swish or any light, shimmery pink also works) – tear duct area and blended on inner crease
benefit high brow pencil – highlight under brow
MAC black tied eyeshadow and fix+ – liner
benefit badgal lash mascara
